——人类仍然可以阻止地球变得更热。若要做到这一点，各国需要协同努力，立即开始迅速放弃化石燃料，到 2050 年左右停止向大气中排放二氧化碳。报告总结说，假使努力见效，全球变暖的过程很可能会停止，但全球气温仍将比工业化前的水平高出 1.5 摄氏度左右。联合国气候报告：全球升温已无法避免，极端天气将大幅增加"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-54f55e6f84ae79699a51761900804231_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "265 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/478518638"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3Nre26vn4N9AEAMaCDY4NjE4NjQxIKqlxIgGMCw4lARAD3IJNDc4NTE4NjM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1628866926.4948268", "card_id": "Q_331404742", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 211}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪个瞬间你会觉得男朋友想跟你结婚只是将就而已？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-4f4f9667e3c0c137f154d13ccf281355_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "244 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/331404742"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3Nre26vn4N9AEAMaCDM1OTIyMjc5IIa7x+gFMAc40QtAEHIJMzMxNDA0NzQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1628866926.4952202", "card_id": "Q_479457307", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "女子被指假死博关注，遭网暴后二次自杀身亡，丈夫称将追责，网暴者需要承担什么样的责任？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "广东惠州。25 岁已婚妈妈唐某被指「假死」博关注，遭网暴后二次自杀身亡。8 月 11 日，丈夫向她生前消费网友的行为道歉，同时表示将追究导致她身亡的网暴者责任。女子被指「假死」遭网暴后二次自杀身亡，丈夫称将追责网暴者 _ 七环视频 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a17c389046c8bc02c25184d224ef1e20_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "233 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479457307"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3Nre26vn4N9AEAMaCDY4ODI3MzY4IIqF2IgGMAQ4owFAEXIJNDc5NDU3MzA3eACqAQliaWx